Package net.opentsdb.rollup

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RollupConfig
    A class that contains the runtime configuration for a TSD's raw and rollup tables.
    RollupConfig.Builder  
    RollUpDataPoint
    Represents a single rolled up data point.
    RollupInterval
    Holds information about a rollup interval.
    RollupInterval.Builder  
    RollupQuery
    Holds information about a rollup interval and rollup aggregator.
    RollupSeq
    Represents a read-only sequence of continuous HBase rows.
    RollupSpan
    Represents a read-only sequence of continuous data points.
    RollupUtils
    Static util class for dealing with parsing and storing rolled up data points
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NoSuchRollupForIntervalException
    Exception thrown when a rollup couldn't be found in the interval to rollup interval map
    NoSuchRollupForTableException
    Exception thrown when a rollup couldn't be found in the table name to rollup interval map
